{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"769b0f251c","title":"给邹普勋、谭熙春、毛锡臣的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ccd21ff2bb","index":0,"year":1953,"month":10,"day":29,"articleId":"769b0f251c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"cb51fcf481","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"769b0f251c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邹普勋，毛泽东少年时的私垫同学和邻居。谭熙春，早年和毛泽东在安源搞过工人运动。毛锡臣，毛泽东的叔祖父。"},{"id":"dec1ddec2f","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"769b0f251c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽连，毛泽东的堂弟。"}],"contents":[{"id":"78178743de","type":"title","text":"给邹普勋、谭熙春、毛锡臣“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"769b0f251c"},{"id":"cb51fcf481","type":"paragraph","text":"邹普勋、谭熙春、毛锡臣同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"769b0f251c"},{"id":"dec1ddec2f","type":"paragraph","text":"你们三位的信都收到了。熙春、锡臣（龙头山的）想来北京一次，普勋想再来北京一次，我想可以。现天气已冷，可在明年开春（阴历三月间）来，如果你们愿意早来，亦可在阳历十二月中句来。由你们三人结伴同行，自己出路费，路上买车票等事亦由自己经理。到京住一个月即回家。如果你们同意，即可照这样办。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"769b0f251c"},{"id":"d86a1886e1","type":"paragraph","text":"此外，我弟毛泽连以（东茅塘的）要求来京治眼病，请邹普勋兄告诉他，亦可同来。除你们四人之外，别人都不要来。如有不得许可，自己来的，不便招待。锡臣、熙春二位不另复，即请普勋兄转致。此间近安","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"769b0f251c"},{"id":"6039eb8014","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"769b0f251c"},{"id":"103d7f28d0","type":"paragraph","text":"十月廿九日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"769b0f251c"}],"page":{"id":"60e0c6d62e","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"769b0f251c","start":419,"end":419}}}},"__N_SSG":true}